- project: finalproject-tps
- language: typescript, react, react-three-fiber
- added: vertical glass-and-steel center separator at x = 0 colored #eef3f6 to match floor slabs, dividing west (BARAT) and east (TIMUR) elevator banks in BuildingScene.tsx.
